{"id":172265,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/贺卫方回应方舟子/","date":"2011-08-15T13:00:32Z","modified":"2011-08-15T13:00:32Z","title":"贺卫方回应方舟子","content":"<p>卢俊义 写道 &#8220;前段时间批评方舟子剽窃的美国学者Root-Bernstein进一步指控方舟子《科学是什么？》一文90%内容抄自他的文章，在此时刻身为打假斗士的方舟子仍拨冗检查了北大法学教授贺卫方的论文发表，方舟子指出贺卫方1993年以来未发表文章，不配当教授。为此贺卫方在博客上列出1990年至2010年发表的论文以及著作及译作。斗士方舟子尚未宣布这些著作合格与否。&#8221;<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1760289c/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E8%B4%BA%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E6%96%B9%E8%88%9F%E5%AD%90&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F08%2F14%2F2344241%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E8%B4%BA%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E6%96%B9%E8%88%9F%E5%AD%90&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F08%2F14%2F2344241%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/110621101350/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1760289c/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/110621101350/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1760289c/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=_3GdGxKrjaQ:2iQ0wF-EZlc:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=_3GdGxKrjaQ:2iQ0wF-EZlc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获